        <h3><strong>Digital Territory Ownership on Sports Fields</strong></h3>
        <p>
          <a href="https://docs.bws.ninja/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fan Game Cube</a> transforms playing fields into tokenized real estate across football, chess, tennis, and cricket. Fans purchase specific coordinates on these fields, becoming digital landlords of precise locations where their favorite sports action unfolds.
