        </p>
        <h3><strong>Event-Based Reward System</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Building on this territorial ownership, the platform continuously tracks real match events and distributes rewards to corresponding NFT holders. When a goal is scored, a chess piece moves, or a tennis ball lands at a specific location, the owner of that field section receives instant rewards.
        </p>
        <p>
